            <div id="comment-17903" class="comment-body clearfix">                    <div class="vcard">
                        <img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/e7569dd973b3e9ae29546666b4e11f18?s=48&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-48 photo' height='48' width='48' />                    </div>
                <div class="comment-author clearfix ">
                    <cite class="fn"><a href='http://catallactick.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>t4li3sin</a></cite>
                    <span class="comment-meta">
                        <a class="rtp-common-link rtp-comment-date" href="http://libertyblitzkrieg.com/2013/11/29/e-gold-founder-is-launching-a-new-gold-backed-currency/#comment-17903" title="November 30, 2013">
